---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Teeth Whitening | Franconia Family Dental"
  description="Professional teeth whitening at Franconia Family Dental. Safe, effective in-office and take-home whitening treatments for a brighter smile in Franconia, NH."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-sky-50 to-white py-16 md:py-24" aria-labelledby="hero-heading">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
        <a href="/services" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-sky-700 hover:text-sky-800 mb-6 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-sky-500 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 rounded">
          <svg aria-hidden="true" class="h-4 w-4 rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
          </svg>
          All Services
        </a>
        <h1 id="hero-heading" class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-5xl">
          Teeth Whitening
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
          A brighter smile can take years off your appearance and dramatically boost
          your confidence. Our professional whitening treatments deliver safe, dramatic
          results that over-the-counter products simply can't match.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="bg-white py-16 md:py-20" aria-labelledby="services-detail-heading">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16 items-start">
        <div>
          <h2 id="services-detail-heading" class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 sm:text-3xl">
            Our Whitening Options
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            We offer two professional whitening options to fit your lifestyle and timeline.
            Both use professional-strength whitening agents that are far more effective
            than anything available over the counter.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-8 space-y-4" role="list">
            {[
              { title: "In-Office Whitening", desc: "Our most powerful option — achieve a smile up to 8 shades brighter in a single one-hour appointment." },
              { title: "Take-Home Whitening Kits", desc: "Custom-fitted trays and professional-strength gel you can use at home on your own schedule." },
              { title: "Combination Treatment", desc: "Start with an in-office treatment and maintain results with a take-home kit." },
              { title: "Sensitivity Management", desc: "We use desensitizing agents to minimize discomfort during and after treatment." },
              { title: "Touch-Up Treatments", desc: "Periodic touch-ups to maintain your bright smile over time." },
            ].map((item) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="flex h-8 w-8 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-100">
                  <svg aria-hidden="true" class="h-4 w-4 text-sky-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <strong class="text-slate-900">{item.title}</strong>
                  <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">{item.desc}</p>
                </div>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-sky-50 p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Why Professional Whitening?</h3>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-3 text-slate-600 text-sm">
              {[
                "Up to 8x more effective than store-bought strips",
                "Custom trays ensure even, consistent results",
                "Supervised by dental professionals for your safety",
                "Faster results — see a difference in one visit",
                "Longer-lasting results with proper maintenance",
              ].map((point) => (
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg aria-hidden="true" class="h-5 w-5 text-sky-700 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                  <span>{point}</span>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Good Candidates for Whitening</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Whitening works best on natural teeth with yellowing or staining from
              coffee, tea, wine, or tobacco. It's less effective on gray staining,
              crowns, veneers, or fillings. We'll evaluate your smile during a
              consultation to ensure whitening is right for you.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="bg-sky-700 py-16" aria-labelledby="cta-heading">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 id="cta-heading" class="text-2xl font-bold text-white sm:text-3xl">Ready for a Brighter Smile?</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-white">Book a whitening consultation and find out which treatment will give you the best results.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
        <a href="/book-appointment" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-white px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-sky-700 shadow-sm transition-all hover:bg-sky-50 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-white focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-sky-700">
          Book Consultation
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+15551234567" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg border-2 border-white bg-transparent px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white transition-all hover:border-white hover:bg-white/10 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-white focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-sky-700">
          <svg aria-hidden="true" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 6.75c0 8.284 6.716 15 15 15h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-1.372c0-.516-.351-.966-.852-1.091l-4.423-1.106c-.44-.11-.902.055-1.173.417l-.97 1.293c-.282.376-.769.542-1.21.38a12.035 12.035 0 01-7.143-7.143c-.162-.441.004-.928.38-1.21l1.293-.97c.363-.271.527-.734.417-1.173L6.963 3.102a1.125 1.125 0 00-1.091-.852H4.5A2.25 2.25 0 002.25 4.5v2.25z" />
          </svg>
          Call (555) 123-4567
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>